Brake point delta.
For each sector, we identify the track distance at which the car’s speed begins monotonically decreasing from the sector’s speed maximum, using the 10 Hz speed trace. A 3-sample Gaussian smoothing is applied before the monotone-descent detection to remove telemetry noise.
